'''Jean-Pierre Mahé''' (21 March 1944, Paris) is a French [[Oriental studies|orientalist]], [[philologist]] and historian of [[Caucasus]], specialist of [[Armenian studies]].<ref name="ASE">{{hy}} Kh. Karadelyan, « Մահե, Ժան-Պիեր Հանրի Մարի » (« Mahé, Jean-Pierre Henri Marie »), in ''[[Armenian Soviet Encyclopedia]]'', vol. VII, [[Armenian National Academy of Sciences]], Erevan, 1981, p.185.</ref>
